PROPOSED SOLUTION

Solution Overview:
Deploy a dedicated Windows Server 2022 reporting infrastructure accessible exclusively through Azure Bastion, providing automated report generation, task scheduling, and secure administration without requiring public IP addresses or VPN infrastructure.

Technical Architecture:

Component 1: Azure Bastion Service
- Secure gateway for RDP access (no VPN needed)
- Browser-based or native client access
- TLS 1.2+ encryption
- Integrated with Entra ID (Azure AD)
- Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) enforcement
- 99.95% SLA uptime guarantee

Component 2: Windows Server 2022 VM
- Dedicated reporting server (no public IP)
- Windows Task Scheduler for automation
- Support for multiple reporting tools
- Private network access only
- Automatic Windows Updates
- Azure Backup integration

Component 3: Reporting Tools
- Power BI Report Server (modern dashboards)
- SQL Server Reporting Services (classic reports)
- PowerShell scripts (custom automation)
- Python environment (data science)
- Email distribution via SMTP

Component 4: Optional Storage
- Azure Files (100GB SMB share)
- Report archival and retention
- Backup and disaster recovery
- Centralized file storage

Security Features:
- No public IP addresses on servers (90% attack surface reduction)
- Zero-trust network architecture
- Entra ID authentication with MFA
- Network Security Groups (NSG) enforcement
- Complete audit logging to Azure Monitor
- Encrypted storage and backups
- Compliance-ready (SOC 2, ISO 27001, HIPAA, PCI DSS)

